# 📊 MedCore EMR: Full Revenue & Cash Flow Model
### 📅 Subscription Tiers: Monthly, Quarterly, 6-Monthly & Yearly

---

## 1. The Strategy: Coverage vs. Growth
To solve your **"Upfront Payment"** concern, we use a **Setup Fee** to zero out your risk on Day 1.

| Component | Your Fixed Cost (Yearly) | Recommended Setup Fee |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| VPS (KVM2) | ₹9,189 | ₹7,000 (Software Set-up) |
| Domain | ₹904 | ₹1,500 (Branding Set-up) |
| Email | ₹485 | ₹1,500 (Communication Set-up) |
| **TOTAL** | **₹10,578** | **₹10,000 – ₹12,000** |

**✅ Result:** The Setup Fee pays for almost your entire first year of infrastructure. Everything you collect in subscriptions is **Pure Profit.**

---

## 2. Subscription Options (The Pricing)
Doctors love flexibility. Giving them "Bulk Discounts" for longer periods is the best way to avoid churn.

| Plan | Price | Equivalent Monthly | Doctor Saves |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Monthly** | **₹2,499** | ₹2,499 | 0% |
| **Quarterly** | **₹6,749** | ₹2,249 | 10% |
| **6-Monthly** | **₹11,999** | ₹1,999 | 20% |
| **Yearly** | **₹19,999** | ₹1,666 | **33% (Most Popular)** |

---

## 3. Cash Flow Analysis: You SPEND vs You GET 
*Based on 1 Client (Dr. Aarti)*

| Interval | You SPEND (Renewal Costs) | You GET (Revenue @ Yearly Plan) | Net Profit |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Day 1** | ₹10,578 (Full Year Paid) | ₹12,000 (Setup) + ₹19,999 (Sub) | **₹21,421** ✅ |
| **Month 1** | ₹0 | ₹0 (Already Paid Yearly) | ₹21,421 |
| **Quarter 1** | ₹0 | ₹0 | ₹21,421 |
| **Year 1 Total** | ₹10,578 | ₹31,999 | **₹21,421** |

### If they pay MONTHLY (₹2,499):
- **Every Month:** You spend ₹0 (it's already paid). You get ₹2,499. Profit accumulates month by month.
- **Year 1 Total:** You get ₹12,000 + (₹2,499 x 12) = ₹41,988. Profit = **₹31,410.**

---

## 4. Scaling the Model: The Power of 10
The magic happens when Dr. Riddhi and 9 others join the **same server.**

| Interval | You SPEND (Cost for 10 Clients) | You GET (Revenue from 10 @ Yearly) | Net Profit |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Every Month** | ₹0 (Renewal is Annual) | ₹0 (If all pay yearly) | — |
| **Every Quarter** | ₹0 | ₹0 | — |
| **Annual Renewal** | **₹23,079** | **₹1,99,990** | **₹1,76,911** |

**Why is cost only ₹23k for 10 people?**
Because you only pay for **1 VPS (₹9,189)** for all 10 people. You only pay for 10 Domains (₹9k) and 10 Emails (₹4.8k).

---

## 🛡️ 5. Your Churn Concern — Re-Validated
**Q: "If I pay for the whole year and the client leaves after 1 month, I lose!"**

**A: NO, look at the math:**
1. **You Collected:** ₹12,000 Setup + ₹2,499 Month 1 = **₹14,499.**
2. **You Paid:** **₹10,578.**
3. **Net even after Churn:** **+₹3,921 Profit.**
4. **The Moat:** Once Dr. Aarti has stored 200 patient records, she **cannot easily leave**. The "switching cost" is too high. You effectively own the clinical workflow.

---

## 🏁 Summary Checklist for your Pitch

1.  **Pitch the Setup Fee:** Tell them it covers the domain registration, security certificate, and custom branding setup.
2.  **Upsell the Yearly Plan:** Tell them they save ₹10,000/year if they pay upfront. This gives you **huge cash flow** to buy more servers.
3.  **The "Complementary" Website:** This is your "Gift" that makes your ₹1,999/month seem like a bargain compared to other EMR brands.
4.  **Security:** Always mention their data is in a private container on a dedicated Hostinger KVM server.

**I have archived this full model for you. You are now armed with both the code and the business logic to win Dr. Aarti's approval!**
